commit_message: Make create_dotplots.Rscript more robust to different envs
correct requirements
update requirements to include minimap2
Fix commented
Fix small error that caused pre-break stats to be overwritten in the stats file.
Add patch_genome.sh to automate two-stage genome patching, with automated contig breaking and before and after dot-plots for all chromosomes.
Cleaned up some cruft
ditch autosave file
Adds scripts for automated rearrangment breakpoint detection and contig breaking.
Adds patch start coordinate within query and query length to contigs.bed
Update documentation for opts.
Removed some unused code and options relevant to the old way of infering contig breakpoints.
Adds handling of overlaps by truncating the overlapping 5-prime end (left overlap) of the 3-prime contig.
Switch to using cigar string to infer alignment space.
Basic handling of overlaps: now drops nested mappings. Overlaps are still bookended for now.

Implments most of linear interval clustering to handle nested/overlapping contigs. Retains commented first-pass of algorithm to do so based on a nested loop over aligments that proved not tractable. This is mainly for historical purposes.
Update defaults to optimal values.
fix typo
Added output section to README.md
Fixed bug causing incorrect entries to be included in patches.bed.
Adds whitelist filter and fixes several bugs.
Fixed bug whereby nested/superimposed reads tricked the script into terminating the alignment space prematurely. Added .gitignore.
Tweak README formatting
Add README.md and __init__.py
Tweak self-documentation
First commit
